{"tid":1565822,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我個藍絲朋友癲左","createTime":"2019-09-13T09:56:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T16:59:50.000Z","uid":287116,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"738d83627243f75c2b608d8d4e200a22e6c24bdd","tid":1565822,"uid":287116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T09:56:29.000Z","msg":"條友之前係深藍，一直話咩支持警察執法，但至從日日學校播榮光後佢開始連歌詞都背左落來，今日仲同我道歉話之前佢太天真Wor<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n願榮光歸香港真係改變到一個人，喚醒佢哋身體內嘅香港人精神！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大家真係要多唱香港國歌！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n願榮光歸香港！<br />\n光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"b51fac05c57186b3e952555e755af5619b5a2dc5","tid":1565822,"uid":156144,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T09:59:36.000Z","msg":"Over咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f352e81c939a40d3983df83bc0bdf5e7e2e053f","tid":1565822,"uid":321315,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T10:04:40.000Z","msg":"係咪真架。好小藍絲會改變到念法。除非被po po 拉过，打过之類。"},{"pid":"f1c0d2980ae668be76507bebadef3a7f6632f85c","tid":1565822,"uid":287116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T10:10:34.000Z","msg":"可能見到黑警頂唔順<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29b9005764b469e1f7d258282568290cd017d94c","tid":1565822,"uid":287116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T10:13:25.000Z","msg":"雖然可能我嗰個係特例，但相信其他人身邊都可能有咁嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />只要努力我地手足就有機會增加，對家就少左人！"},{"pid":"34532979f23ab1d671e9f6239d11a23309e520a9","tid":1565822,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T16:59:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由